headline: 3 Outsourcing Stocks to Consider Despite Industry Headwinds
summary: The Zacks Outsourcing industry is well-positioned to gain from rising demand for business process outsourcing and AI and ML. PAYX, G, and BBSI are three stocks that are prime candidates to ride the demand wave.
